{"tid":1417964,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想場運動贏的話，麻煩聽聽梁天綺講，be humble！","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:26:57.000Z","uid":34296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4dfcdbcc9a9dd26da10a2de60821b8cf60a7468","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"其實今日玩火失民意都唔緊要<br />\n都係失左班無係現場既和理非同淺黃既支持<br />\n<br />\n但係仲有班係現場食花生既師奶 伯伯係現場<br />\n佢地好多都支持你地 但又想打下卡比班朋友睇下<br />\n<br />\n佢地可能影相係唔岩 因為有藍絲曾經影相點相<br />\n所以現場有影相係要阻止 但你無做犯法野時 <br />\n我覺得可以比佢地影下 等佢地感受下班後生仔明明和和平平都比你班警犬吠 <br />\n<br />\n我相信蝴蝶效應 當你地兇走左個師奶or廢老 就即係兇走左一班人 但如果大家禮貌地問句&ldquo;樓上係唔係影緊相呀？&rdquo;or &ldquo;樓上既市民可唔可以唔好影我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rdquo;<br />\n會好過講句 &ldquo;喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪撚影啦屌你老母&rdquo;<br />\n大家唔好再濫用屌你老母 但當然個廢老當你耳邊風就梗係要屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發過好多次夢都見到示威者情緒好易暴躁 比藍絲挑釁下就好似警犬咁發癲 藍絲係黑人憎 但係大家都要忍 唔忍就會輸左場運動<br />\n<br />\n另外隔離有幾個post都話警犬禮貌左 同埋係時候要將場運動既模式變少少 但唔洗改口號 唔洗無暴力 <br />\n只要大家學識同警犬鬥玩be humble同be smart<br />\n咁場運動又會傾向返大家到<br />\n<br />\n認真 場運動失民意就輸一半 而今日可以行到呢一步都係因為民意一致 <br />\n今日既行動其實明顯失左部分民意 但大家都不割庶 如果想贏返民意 麻煩大家控制下情緒 屌狗可以 但對市民就收收火<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce5c5441dd54d6b32e5926554c2577c28f42f1fa","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"大家可以討論下"},{"pid":"e72d5362059ab01e040f5217a6bfa74f791ee504","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"我唔想最後場運動又輸 但又犧牲左400幾個義士"},{"pid":"58241f8ee69e25f86c7cfd7946f64345776602f7","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"大家想行動升級都要be smart<br />\n要有原因講服到班和理非支持你地 <br />\n因為和理非係場運動佔一大半"},{"pid":"c4db6fa9d40e2190c82bafaee92a3d515de3498d","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"我地要連班中立撚都要吸納返"},{"pid":"ce307805b58d3d0612986860dd1f1ef08927f78c","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920b71b49b18c407d115e41171bba5e2b4f3140a","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"比返啲禮貌出黎啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dc5a89bd91c55b9bc7ac8623f577be9dc28a44","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:21.000Z","msg":"同埋好唔再用雷射亂照人 要照都集中照犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989840461d314d6f62efb84fc9c455e51821b018","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"想叫遠處人唔好影相可以嗌特徵<br />\n例如上面/前面短髮/長髮黑衫/藍衫/個位女士/男士<br />\n<br />\n唔好影我地相呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d0550ce11e3670c0bb7534b98ab400a62d8b6a","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"你地學懂尊重人 別人就懂得尊重你<br />\n<br />\n除非對方係藍絲 如果係藍絲就當佢發up風<br />\n佢打你既時候唔好還手住 睇情況<br />\n最好無人拍住你個陣先還手<br />\n有人拍既時候 其他手足麻煩捉住佢入一入鏡<br />\n話佢知打人唔岩"},{"pid":"6d2aa9aa93017e2b5fcd811aed521ebb142182c4","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:38.000Z","msg":"場運動唔係淨係勇武或者行動升級就會玩贏林鄭 逼到佢出黎<br />\n要玩就同佢玩腦"},{"pid":"84d0aa970ac6db09314c848557edc12e2554b235","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:56:27.000Z","msg":"另外想講<br />\n林鄭次次都係行動升級先走出黎指責<br />\n但又唔回應民間訴求<br />\n想用指責義士去蒙混自己問題<br />\n<br />\n而呢個方法又引到大家嬲嬲豬之餘 逼到大家非升級不可 等大家自己搞衰場運動 <br />\n<br />\n最後佢雖然都係無哂民望 但係我地都比佢搞到失敗之餘 仲要承擔失敗後既後果"},{"pid":"a64033ecbefe7a6f2fa757ef0ca657d3636982d3","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b7c8a61b94a462f5710e23fe81bea7f7bfeb0b08","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"我地同林鄭一樣都唔會認輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25d211add190223dd80cac54252c8762231a065","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b8c55e7f4f38d3aa0296d4de83298ca5067648","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec7ab1706048a08716d9605a67d840c34ab91d4","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"0700964eb8f693e8bea7efda17ede8c64e01280c","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭你食屎啦"},{"pid":"a6dcbe278907df6ced644d1438d2990fa40c9ef2","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:59:56.000Z","msg":"黑社會同打市民既垃圾都希望你地臨老過唔到世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cbc68cd1cef9e50148313ea8e746d5fdd6cfac","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:14.000Z","msg":"周身病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637c0357f0426f465d78a58dc6caff3e0fdf012a","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"比共雞呃身雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcea928bf5090d83b9dd6bc5de2b6cf05758bead","tid":1417964,"uid":34296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b03e3d0867a222c680565e7d82404f685750ae8","tid":1417964,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"[形象工程] 我們不是暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1428424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1428424</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"103e8e9ebdacf2edbe455e0bdb2a8c0036ea0f3d","tid":1417964,"uid":112164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"Be humble be smart"}]}